                     <interp inst="t17840915-58-person724" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , PETER BOND,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840915-58-verdict291" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-58-verdict291" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Each to be <rs id="t17840915-58-punish292" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-58-punish292" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
